          "slidecontent": "• AI can generate and spread convincing false content faster than humans can fact-check it\n• Emotional, outrage-driven stories are amplified by algorithms because they drive engagement\n• Deepfakes and synthetic media make it harder to trust what you see or hear\n• Always verify before sharing\n• Credible sources, reverse image searches, and fact-checking sites are your best tools\n• Building the habit of pausing before sharing is the single most effective step you can take right now"
